    "7301615": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Arabalika",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Phew... That was scary! It's a good thing that Arabalika helped out."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arabalika",
                    "T": "Arabalika told you so. Paimon is careless. Will get in trouble."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Alright, alright... Paimon's got it..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Ruin Guards are here to do their job too, you know."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yeah, guards should be guarding something against trespassers. After all, we're outsiders to them."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arabalika",
                    "T": "#Nara {NICKNAME} and Paimon are outsiders to Vana. Not Arabalika. The Huge Iron Chunk is making no sense."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arabalika",
                    "T": "Arabalika will teach it sense."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Woah... Um, Paimon will become more sensible in the future!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I'll hold you to your word, Paimon."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Of course! Tomorrow... No, starting from now!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arabalika",
                    "T": "#Only Aranara can awaken the stone here. Leave the rest to Arabalika, Nara {NICKNAME} and Paimon."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Ooooh!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "We're one step closer to healing the Varuna Contraption! Once it is healed, there won't be so many spores in Apam Woods anymore... Just thinking about it makes Paimon's nose itch..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arabalika",
                    "T": "The Varuna Contraption will purify rainwater. There will not be black rain or so many spores."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arabalika",
                    "T": "But there should still be mushrooms. Be careful, Paimon. You might get eaten by them. Like Aranakula."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yes... Paimon'll be careful!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arabalika",
                    "T": "#Arabalika no longer needed here. Arabalika will return to the \"rest stop\" to look for Arapandu. Nara {NICKNAME} and Paimon, will you return with Arabalika?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Let's go together."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arabalika",
                    "T": "Yes. It is dangerous in Vana. Traveling together is safer."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I have something else to do."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arabalika",
                    "T": "#Be careful, Nara {NICKNAME} and Paimon. Don't be careless. May Aramuhukunda watch over you."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
