    "7301511": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Aranakula",
        "Step": "Now that the visible memories that Aranara left for Nara Varuna have been cleaned up, it is time to proceed to heal the \"branch\" and \"leaves.\"",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Aranakula",
                    "T": "#Oh! Thank you, Nara {NICKNAME}!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranakula",
                    "T": "Vana remembers everything that happened after Nara Varuna arrived. Big trees remember and seeds remember, but we don't know if Nara Varuna will understand..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranakula",
                    "T": "That's why we left visible memories. This way, when Nara Varuna returns, Nara Varuna will know that Vana never forgets and Aranara never forget."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Now, Paimon understands... So the Memory of Stone is a memorial plaque. Well, humans also erect memorial monuments, so that they don't forget things."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Well, Nara are forgetful creatures."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "...Compared to the forest, Nara are like small plants that will never become towering trees. They won't ever have tree rings that remember everything..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranakula",
                    "T": "Aranara won't leave Vana. Aranara will always be with Vana. But Nara come and Nara go, just like Nara Varuna."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranakula",
                    "T": "There are many Aranara, just like how there are many big trees in Vana. Many Aranara and many names, just like how there are many branches on a tree."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranakula",
                    "T": "Golden Nara remembers many Aranara names and remembers that I am Aranakula. It is like picking up a floating leaf and knowing which tree it is from."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#Nara Varuna must also have been a special Nara to the Aranara — that's why they erected a monument for {M#her}{F#him}."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Well, it's not quite the same, but we've seen statues with specific faces carved onto them before, haven't we?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "...You mean the Statues of The Seven?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#Yeah! And now that we've heard Nara Varuna's story, {NICKNAME}, don't you want to know what {F#he}{M#she} looks like?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Aranara have music, so it's possible that they are also skilled in other areas! Maybe they can make lifelike statues too or something..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I'd love to see them if they have any."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Right? Hehe, Nara Varuna, a Golden Nara..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Aranara art is very simple, so it's difficult to imagine..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hmm... Or you know, their art could just be too advanced for you..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Ooh, right! Guess we can go and heal the Varuna Contraption's branches and leaves now, right?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranakula",
                    "T": "#Yes. Aranakula will bring Nara {NICKNAME} and Paimon there."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "7301512": {
        "Desc": "Find the \"branch\" together with Aranakula",
        "Talk": []
    },
    "7301513": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Aranakula",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "So this is where it was hidden. Wow, we might not have found this place without Aranakula leading the way..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "But where are its leaves? Paimon doesn't see them."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranakula",
                    "T": "The leaves... They are near this big tree, but..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hmm... The Fungi won't find their way in, so this place is safe. You can just wait for us here, Aranakula!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Arapandu told us we just need to make the \"leaves\" on the three stones turn toward the \"branch,\" right?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranakula",
                    "T": "#Thank you, Nara {NICKNAME} and Paimon."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "7301514": {
        "Desc": "Make the three \"leaves\" turn towards the \"branch\"",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Aranakula",
                    "T": "Once the Varuna Contraption is fixed, the bad seeds will be no more, and many flowers will grow in the nurseries..."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "7301516": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Aranakula",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Aranakula, we're back! You'll need to handle the rest from here though."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranakula",
                    "T": "#Thank you, Paimon, and thank you, Nara {NICKNAME}. Aranakula knows what to do."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh! It looks like everything will be fine here too."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I hope the forest will return to normal soon."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranakula",
                    "T": "It will once the Varuna Contraption is fixed. But Marana... must be eliminated for Vana and Sarva."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranakula",
                    "T": "Just as the monument made for Nara Varuna has been covered by bad seeds, Ashvattha's Concourses have also been affected by Marana."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranakula",
                    "T": "There was a time before Nara Varuna came to Vanarana. Nara and Aranara made nurseries together then. But now..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Now, only the children of Vimara Village can still see you. To adults, you only exist in stories... And the nurseries you talked about have also become deserted because of Marana..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranakula",
                    "T": "Aranakula wants to fill the nurseries with flowers. Nara have forgotten Aranara, but it's fine. Nara will see the flowers."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Aranakula..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranakula",
                    "T": "#Nara {NICKNAME}, Paimon, thank you. Aranakula won't forget."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranakula",
                    "T": "Aranakula will return to the \"rest stop\" now. Arapandu will be happy to know that the monument is now clean."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranakula",
                    "T": "#Will Nara {NICKNAME} and Paimon return to the \"rest stop\" with Aranakula?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Sure."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranakula",
                    "T": "Traveling with Golden Nara feels so safe."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I have something else to do."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranakula",
                    "T": "#May Aramuhukunda watch over Nara {NICKNAME} and Paimon. Don't get eaten by bad guys."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
