    "7301802": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Arapandu",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Arapandu",
                    "T": "#Nara {NICKNAME}, and Paimon, thank you for helping Aranara. Arapandu senses that the branches blocking the stream in various places have been removed."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh! So we can go and heal the Varuna Contraption now, right?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arapandu",
                    "T": "Soon, but not yet. The root system is deep underground, and the entrance is in the center of the Varunastra."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "The Varunastra... You've mentioned that before, haven't you, Arapandu?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arapandu",
                    "T": "#It's a manifestation of the power of the Varuna Contraption. When it displays its power, it will be taller than the tallest tree in Vana. Nara {NICKNAME} and Paimon saw it before."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Do you mean that place from which water jets out occasionally? Are we seriously going through the center of that thing!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "That doesn't look like an entrance."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "That's right!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "We can't get in! There's no way to get in!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hey!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "What if it activates just as we go in...?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "The water jet is so high, and it looks really powerful too... Paimon can't figure out how we're going to get into its center..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Guess we can only get in from above."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Well, Paimon can fly, but you sure can't!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "So we're taking this thing head-on, then."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Paimon's heard that some people train by sitting under a waterfall and absorbing its impact... But we'll surely be swept away if we just rush in!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Maybe we can dig a tunnel to it from the side..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "What kind of solution is that? ... Wait. It might be worth a try..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arabalika",
                    "T": "Why? We can just make it stop."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "It can stop!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arapandu",
                    "T": "#It couldn't before, but thanks to Nara {NICKNAME} and Paimon's help, the power of the Varuna Contraption has been partially restored. Now, Aranara can make it stop."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Wow, we did such an amazing thing by coincidence!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Well, it's not so much of a coincidence..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Ah, true. It was really difficult to find the Grove of Dreams..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Paimon is amazing!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "You're amazing too. Hehe, we're both amazing!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arapandu",
                    "T": "#Nara {NICKNAME}, Paimon, let's go together. The green branches have bloomed. It's almost time to bear fruit."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
