    "7301805": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "It's even more impressive when you see it up close..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arapandu",
                    "T": "The Varuna Contraption is a creation of the Lord of Dendro. It sends forth water that brings life, turning Valuka into Vana, replacing that which was once yellow with green, and turning barren land into a land full of life."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "It sounds miraculous. \"Water that brings life\"... Wow..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Speaking of which, Paimon ate the soup Arapas made earlier. That was made with the water from here, right?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "His soup doesn't have a special effect, right..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Maybe it reverses aging."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh? Would that happen you, or Paimon?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "It'd be you, baby Paimon."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "If Paimon gets any younger than she is now..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You'd become like a Cicin."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh come on, Paimon won't become *that* small!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Couldn't be me, right?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "If that's the case..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#Hah, \"Good baby {NICKNAME}, Paimon's here to take care of you! C'mere, let Paimon give you some hugsy-wugsies!\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "It might let you live forever."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Wow, it might be possible to live long enough to eat every dish in Teyvat that way!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "But where will those who share the taste be then...?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hmm... Guess living too long is not entirely a good thing, huh..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranakula",
                    "T": "So Paimon wants water..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranakula",
                    "T": "If Paimon becomes a seed, Aranakula will take good care of her, water her properly, and put her in a sunny place and loosen the soil for her."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arakunti",
                    "T": "Arakunti will play music to Paimon and tell her things about Vana that she doesn't know."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arakunti",
                    "T": "Arabalika won't come to see Paimon so often. But will bring mushrooms. Cook for her."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arabalika",
                    "T": "Arabalika will not do such things."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Ooh, that sure sounds like such a cozy life! ...Wait! Paimon won't turn into a seed! What is this, some kind of scary forest that you can't leave once you enter!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "...It's even scarier when you think that these words are coming from these sweet-looking Aranara!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You'll grow strong and bear fruit quickly, Paimon."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hey! Don't you start saying that scary stuff too!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arapandu",
                    "T": "Nara and Paimon won't stay in Vana like Aranara do. Aranakula knows this."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Aranakula",
                    "T": "#Aranakula knows... Nara {NICKNAME} and Paimon have other missions and will leave Vana, like other Nara..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arapandu",
                    "T": "We have to complete the Aranara mission now and stop the Varuna Contraption in order to go down and remove those bad bugs and heal the machine."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
